{"tid":939004,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"「慈雲山撚」邊個醫生最伏","createTime":"2018-12-12T17:57:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T11:02:47.000Z","uid":15894,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c38917736c616aea8fb4bcfea1da47ba775d6e65","tid":939004,"uid":15894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T17:57:49.000Z","msg":"慈雲山醫生好多。以前睇開果個退左休，<br />\n陳嘉x醫生，聽人講串77，睇baby kingdom又話佢無醫德。今日一去睇簡直無人品 ，先唔講醫術 ，個人修養已經好差，醫者父母心 ，但佢把口完全唔尊重人。<br />\n睇睇下病又查書又剩 ，又轉介你睇專科收你轉介科。上網睇原來佢又用同一段。<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote> <a href=\"https://www.baby-kingdom.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=9342226\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.baby-kingdom.com%2Fforum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D9342226&d=ShSKjGv5XJTGcqIQG8d37V0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=f441213b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.baby-kingdom.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=9342226</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0b8fba9e09948c36a589e29d36592759b4e4767f","tid":939004,"uid":15894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T18:51:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d5ddb30bb604d5726a1ba04d093f2255736d864","tid":939004,"uid":23271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T19:15:36.000Z","msg":"何志申<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ad19621a8f4dc437a82ec13576f449afb5a6446","tid":939004,"uid":26505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c38917736c616aea8fb4bcfea1da47ba775d6e65","tid":939004,"uid":15894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T17:57:49.000Z","msg":"慈雲山醫生好多。以前睇開果個退左休，<br />\n陳嘉x醫生，聽人講串77，睇baby kingdom又話佢無醫德。今日一去睇簡直無人品 ，先唔講醫術 ，個人修養已經好差，醫者父母心 ，但佢把口完全唔尊重人。<br />\n睇睇下病又查書又剩 ，又轉介你睇專科收你轉介科。上網睇原來佢又用同一段。<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote> <a href=\"https://www.ba